Module jdk.jdi
Package com.sun.jdi

Interface FloatValue

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable<FloatValue>, Mirror, PrimitiveValue, Value
public interface FloatValue
extends PrimitiveValue, Comparable<FloatValue>
Provides access to a primitive float value in the target VM.
Since:
1.3
